title: INSIGHT: Taiwan's festival of firecrackers
text:
INSIGHT: Taiwan's festival of firecrackers Tuesday, March 06, 2018 - 01:03 
Participants wearing motorcycle helmets and makeshift protective gear get sprayed with firecrackers during the annual 'Beehive Firecrackers' festival in Taiwan. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
